{
  "texts": [
    "suggested a framework based on deep learning algorithms to extract event-related information such as the date, location, and type of accident from accident news reports (Feng and Chen, 2021).",
    "On the other hand, Rupasinghe et al.",
    "proposed a rule-based technique to extract hazard-related information from accident reports (Rupasinghe and Panuwatwanich, 2021).",
    "Similarly, (Baker et al., 2020) suggested using Natural Language Processing (NLP) techniques to identify injury precursors.",
    "However, there is still a lack of research focused on automatically extracting requirements from construction safety rules to ensure compliance in the field."
  ]
}